                Bonae memoriae Maccusae <lb n="2"/>Muceris <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>orum</ex></expan> XXII et Victoriae <lb n="3"/>sive Valeriosae <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>orum</ex></expan> XIIII quae <lb n="4"/>ob desiderium avunculi eorum <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>Fl</abbr><ex>avi</ex></expan> Gemelli <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>iri</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>erfectissimi</ex></expan> comitis ab ultima <lb n="6"/>Gallia per diversa loca provin<lb break="no" n="7"/>ciarum ad provinciam Macedo<lb break="no" n="8"/>niam venerunt <expan><abbr>ibidemq</abbr><ex>ue</ex></expan> post am<lb break="no" n="9"/>plexum eius et completa cupiditate <lb n="10"/>amoris in civitat&amp;lt;e=I&amp;gt; &amp;lt;E=I&amp;gt;d&amp;lt;e=I&amp;gt;ssensi fati munus <lb n="11"/>compleverunt quibus memoratus <lb n="12"/>vir laudabilis ut cognoscere<lb break="no" n="13"/>tur iussit eis memoriam fieri 
